burning%2C%20whole%20of%20India%20is%20burning%2C%20if%20Manipur%20is%20divided%2C%20the%20country%20is%20divided.%20It%20was%20our%20demand%20that%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20should%20come%20to%20the%20House%20and%20speak%20about%20Manipur.%20However%2C%20he%20kept%20a%20'maun%20vrat%20(vow%20of%20silence)%20that%20he%20will%20neither%20speak%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20nor%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gogoi%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EParliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-didnt-he-speak-first-ministers-dig-at-rahul-gandhi-on-no-trust-debate-4279152%5C%22%3EPralhad%20Joshi%20wondered%3C%2Fa%3E%20why%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20name%20as%20lead%20speaker%20was%20withdrawn%20last%20minute.%20Congress%20sources%20had%20earlier%20said%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20freshly%20reinstated%20in%20parliament%2C%20would%20open%20the%20debate.%20Sources%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20won't%20speak%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-confidence-vote-live-no-trust-motion-in-lok-sabha-latest-no-trust-motion-will-test-opposition-unity-pms-swipe-ahead-of-big-vote-4278921%5C%22%3EPM%20Modi%20in%20the%20BJP%20parliamentary%20meeting%20earlier%20this%20morning%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20this%20is%20not%20a%20vote%20to%20express%20distrust%20in%20the%20government%2C%20but%20to%20see%20who%20can%20trust%20who%20in%20the%20opposition.%20Targetting%20former%20Congress%20chief%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20he%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20now%20has%20only%20two%20jobs.%20'Set'%20the%20son%20and%20give%20presents%20to%20the%20son-in-law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGaurav%20Gogoi's%20response%20that%20should%20the%20remarks%20made%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla's%20chamber%20be%20revealed%20in%20the%20House%20evoked%20a%20