om%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-after-vacating-delhi-bungalow-price-for-speaking-truth-3970494%5C%22%3Epunished%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20for%20speaking%20the%20truth%20and%20said%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20live%20in%20the%20house%20anymore%20since%20the%20bungalow%2C%20given%20to%20him%20by%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bsnatched%20away%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20ordered%20a%20stay%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20conviction%20and%20said%20that%20while%20his%20remarks%20were%20not%20in%20good%20taste%2C%20his%20disqualification%20from%20parliament%20would%20affect%20his%20constituents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20court%20order%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-to-visit-wayanad-on-aug-12-13-4279386%5C%22%3Ethe%20Wayanad%20MP%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20back%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20parliament%20is%20witnessing%20repeated%20disruptions%20over%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA's%20demand%20for%20a%20dedicated%20discussion%20on%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20prefaced%20by%20PM%20Modi's%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20was%20disqualified%20in%20March%20after%20he%20was%20awarded%20a%20two-year%20jail%20term%20in%20the%20defamation%20case%20over%20his%20comments%20about%20PM%20Modi's%20surname.%20At%20a%20rally%20in%20Karnataka's%20Kolar%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20general%20election%2C%20in%20a%20dig%20at%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20come%20all%20the%20thieves%20have%20'Modi'%20as%20the%20common%20surname%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691489400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fq2v3glto_rahul-gandhi-home-1200_650x400_08_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-gets-his-bungalow-back-after-being-reinstated-as-mp-sources-4279562%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20r