dnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Biggest%20Match-Winner%2C%20Wins%2050%25%20Of%20Matches%5C%22%3A%20Kaif%20On%20India%20Superstar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20cricketer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammad%20Kaif%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F247-mohammad-kaif-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Kaif%3C%2Fa%3E%20asserted%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20Indian%20team%20has%20the%20capability%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%20this%20year%20and%20it%20should%20not%20be%20judged%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20two%20T20I%20losses%20in%20the%20West%20Indies.%20India%2C%20after%20winning%20the%20two-Test%20series%20and%20ODIs%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20are%20trailing%200-2%20in%20the%20five-match%20T20I%20series%2C%20leading%20to%20criticism%20over%20the%20side's%20preparations%20ahead%20of%20two%20major%20competitions%20--%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20at%20home.%20However%2C%20Kaif%20said%20at%20a%20function%20here%20that%20the%20fears%20of%20India%20under-performing%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20were%20unfounded%2C%20although%20he%20indicated%20that%20pace%20bowler%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20have%20to%20be%20fully%20fit%20for%20the%20hosts%20to%20end%20the%20title%20drought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20lost%20just%20two%20matches%20(T20Is%20against%20West%20Indies)%2C%20so%20we%20do%20not%20need%20to%20get%20overly%20concerned.%20I%20am%20seeing%20a%20lot%20of%20negative%20reaction%20after%20the%20two%20losses.%20But%20I%20will%20only%20say%20that%20our%20team%20is%20extremely%20competitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20going%20to%20judge%20(India)%20on%20two%20back-to-back%20losses%20(in%20the%20West%20Indies).%20The%20only%20thing%20is%20that%20key%20players%20are%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBumrah%20missing%20is%20the%20biggest%20factor.%20If%20he%20recovers%20fully...%20one%20aspect%20is%20to%20complete%20the%20recovery%20and%20the%20other%20aspect%20is%20to%20gain%20match%20fitness.%20If%20he%20regains%20that%20(match%20fitness)%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20massive%20gain%20for%20Team%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Bumrah%20is%20fully%20fit%2C%20we%20have%20a%20great%20chance%20of%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kaif.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20will%20be%20staging%20a%20comeback%20during%20the%20T20%20series%20against%20Ireland%20after%20being%20out%20of%20action%20for%20almost%20a%20year%20following%20a%20back%20surgery%2C%20and%20Kaif%20attributed%20the%2029-year-old%20quick's%20absence%20for%20India's%20string%20of%20losses%20in%20major%20competitions%20during%20that%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20discussing%20that%20the%20(India)%20team%20under%20(chief%20coach)%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20lost%20the%20(T20)%20Asia%20Cup%20(last%20year)%2C%20the%20(T20)%20World%20Cup%20in%20Australia%2C%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20in%20England%20(recently).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20understand%20all%20that%2C%20mistakes%20have%20happened.%20But%20I%20think%2C%20is%20it%20not%20easy%20to%20play%20with%20Bumrah%20not%20in%20the%20side.%20He%20is%20the%20biggest%20match-winner%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20get%20his%20services%2C%20so%20think%20about%20all%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20Bumrah%20returns%20fully%20fit...%20he%20wins%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20matches%20for%20the%20Indian%20team.%20I%20think%20if%20Bumrah%20is%20in%20the%20team%20and%20a%20few%20others%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20return%2C%20we%20have%20the%20players%20who%20can%20win%20the%20(World%20Cup)%20trophy%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Kaif.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20players%20will%20have%20to%20wait%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20youngsters%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112646-yashasvi-jaiswal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fa%3E%20giving%20impressive%20performances%20in%20the%20series%20against%20the%20West%20Indies%2C%20there%20has%20been%20talk%20about%20them%20being%20considered%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20India%2C%20but%20Kaif%20felt%20when%20the%20likes%20of%20Bumrah%2C%20Iyer%2C%20Rahul%20return%20to%20the%20side%2C%20even%20someone%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammed%20Siraj%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107503-mohammed-siraj-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Siraj%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20find%20a%20place%20in%20the%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShreyas%20Iyer%20is%20injured%2C%20KL%20Rahul%20is%20recovering.%20I%20hope%20they%20will%20all%20return%20to%20the%20side%20(in%20time%20for%20the%20World%20Cup).%20So%20all%20this%20talk%20about%20new%20players%20coming%20into%20the%20side%20(for%20the%20World%20Cup)%2C%20they%20will%20not%20get%20a%20chance%20in%20the%20team.%20Your%20(Team%20India's)%20XI%20is%20all%20set%2C%26quot%3B%20averred%20Kaif.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIy