9s%20opponents%2C%20and%20deflated%20his%20party%20and%20its%20followers.%20In%20the%20foreseeable%20future%2C%20this%20is%20likely%20to%20bring%20Modi%20difficulties%20and%20serious%20challenges%20%E2%80%93%20from%20his%20opponents%2C%20but%20probably%20also%20from%20within%20his%20own%20political%20and%20ideological%20universe%20if%20things%20slide%20some%20more%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20this%20awareness%20that%20now%20appears%20to%20make%20the%20prime%20minister%20more%20aggressive%20even%20by%20the%20standards%20of%20aggression%20against%20opponents%20(from%20within%20his%20own%20party%20and%20outside)%20that%20he%20has%20cultivated%20through%20his%20political%20career%20%E2%80%93%20first%20in%20his%20home%20state%20Gujarat%20and%20then%20in%20the%20national%20sphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardly%20a%20day%20passes%20when%2C%20irrespective%20of%20context%2C%20he%20does%20not%20seek%20to%20mount%20crass%20linguistic%20offensives%20against%20INDIA%2C%20the%20opposition%20parties%20grouping%20that%20includes%20the%20Congress%2C%20sinking%20to%20juvenile%20levels%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20Saturday%2C%20for%20example%2C%20while%20green-lighting%20the%20renovation%20of%20506%20railway%20stations%20online%2C%20Modi%20went%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-opposition-criticism-pm-modis-quit-india-jab-over-dynasty-politics-4276259%5C%22%3Eask%20his%20listeners%20to%20%E2%80%98Quit%20India%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20play%20on%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement%20that%20began%20on%20August%209%2C%201942%2C%20a%20historical%20anti-colonial%20tide%20with%20which%20the%20RSS%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20mother%20ship%2C%20had%20conspicuously%20refused%20to%20associate%20itself%20because%20it%20was%20busy%20playing%20pro-British%20politics%20in%20that%20era%2C%20severely%20denting%20its%20claim%20to%20Indian%20nationalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENarendra%20Modi%20ko%20gussa%20kyon%20ata%20hai%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20Why%20is%20Narendra%20Modi%20angry%3F%20The%20answer%20lies%20in%20plain%20sight%3A%20For%20the%20first%20time%20since%20he%20entered%20politics%2C%20Modi%20finds%20himself%20up%20against%20a%20determined%2C%20steely%2C%20ideological%20opponent%2C%20one%20who%20cannot%20be%20frightened%20or%20bribed%20and%20who%20goes%20out%20into%20the%20open%20and%20exposes%20the%20truth%20about%20the%20Modi%20regime%20as%20he%20sees%20it%20%E2%80%93%20and%20this%20is%20done%20with%20a%20rare%20boldness%20and%20vigour%2C%20making%20the%20strongman%20anxious%20that%20a%20third%20term%20as%20prime%20minister%2C%20that%20he%20so%20hankers%20after%2C%20may%20yet%20elude%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20core%20ideology%20of%20confronting%20the%20RSS-BJP%20goal%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20as%20articulated%20by%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20of%20transforming%20this%20country%20of%20multiple%20exegeses%2C%20traditions%20and%20pathways%20to%20life%2C%20thought%20and%20politics%2C%20into%20a%20gigantic%20prison-house%20of%20supremacist%20thought%20of%20the%20religious%20majority%20in%20which%20deviations%20are%20punished%20with%20violence%2C%20is%20what%20has%20irked%20the%20prime%20minister%20most%20about%20his%20much%20younger%20opponent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20supremacist%20thought%20and%20action%20is%20hard%20to%20divorce%20from%20the%20nurturing%20of%20big%20business%20interests%20in%20Indian%20conditions%2C%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20probably%20the%20best%20illustration%20of%20this%2C%20Gandhi%20has%20unfailingly%20directed%20his%20energies%20to%20challenging%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20policy%20orientation%20which%20has%20brought%20widespread%20suffering%20upon%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20less%20privileged%20sections%20of%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20session%20of%20Parliament%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%E2%80%99s%20gut%20punch%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20on%20his%20apparently%20closer%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-modi-adani-parliament%5C%22%3Eclose%20purported%20association%20with%20the%20tycoon%20Gautam%20Adani%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20proximate%20cause%20that%20led%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20to%20do%20its%20best%20to%20seek%20his%20removal%20from%20the%20political%20scene%2C%20although%20almost%20his%20entire%20speech%20was%20expunged%20from%20the%20records%20by%20a%20ruling%20party%20that%20seems%20to%20fear%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20forays%20into%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20backdrop%20to%20the%20fearsome%20Parliament%20speech%20was%20the%20Congress%20leader%E2%80%99s%20dramatic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-yatra-public-action-congress%5C%22%3EBharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20nearly%204%2C000-kilometre-long%20march%20joined%20by%20thousands%2C%20in%20the%20course%20of%20which%20he%20pressed%20his%20belief%20in%20communal%20harmony%20and%20peace%2C%20and%20the%20upliftment%20of%20the%20poorer%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20was%20overnight%20transformed%20into%20a%20hero%20after%20the%20feat%2C%20a%20champion%20of%20the%20masses%2C%20shedding%20his%20earlier%20image%20of%20a%20lackadaisical%2C%20uninterested%20politician%20and%20dynast.%20Modi%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20went%20from%20being%20a%20mass%20leader%20to%20a%20vengeful%20power-seeker%20out%20to%20use%20underhand%20means%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20opponents%20to%20gain%20his%20objective%20as%20he%20went%20about%20mounting%20majoritarian%20war%20through%20the%20agency%20of%20lumpen%20armed%20gangs%20as%20the%20state%20looked%20away%2C%20giving%20tax%20breaks%20to%20the%20super-rich%2C%20and%20keeping%20an%20uncaring%20silence%20as%20small%20and%20big%20fires%20burnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20arguing%20for%20the%20staying%20of%20conviction%20in%20the%20criminal%20defamation%20case%2C%20apart%20from%20advancing%20legal%20and%20technical%20arguments%2C%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20had%20urged%20that%20he%20was%20within%20his%20rights%2C%20as%20an%20opposition%20figure%2C%20to%20criticise%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20his%20government%2C%20and%20that%20this%20is%20what%20he%20had%20done.%20With%20the%20appeal%20being%20upheld%20by%20the%20top%20court%2C%20the%20message%20will%20go%20out%20across%20the%20board%20that%20in%20a%20democracy%20it%20is%20legitimate%20%E2%80%93%20indeed%20necessary%20%E2%80%93%20to%20criticise%20the%20leader%20of%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20punches%20a%20hole%20into%20the%20assumption%20carefully%20cultivated%20by%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20that%20authoritarian%20rule%20is%20natural%20in%20a%20country%20such%20as%20India%20where%20people%20desire%20a%20so-called%20strong%20government.%20Its%20corollary%20%E2%80%93%20the%20invincibility%20of%20Modi%20and%20the%20placing%20of%20the%20ruler%20above%20criticism%20as%20in%20the%20long%20discarded%20feudal%20order%20of%20yore%20%E2%80%93%20now%20lies%20discredited%20even%20as%20an%20argument.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20reports%20suggest%20that%20Gandhi%20will%20take%20part%20in%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20debate%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20country%20will%20be%20all%20ears%2C%20and%20the%20treasury%20benches%20will%20have%20anxious%20moments.%20Modi%20will%20no%20doubt%20be%20worrying%20about%20how%20to%20tackle%20this%20unexpected%20turn%20of%20events.%20Will%20the%20censor%E2%80%99s%20red%20pencil%20be%20applied%20once%20again%20to%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20speech%2C%20as%20it%20had%20been%20when%20he%20tore%20into%20the%20prime%20minister%20on%20the%20Adani%20affair%20following%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20is%2C%20then%20there%20could%20be%20political%20turmoil%2C%20with%20silent%20resentment%20already%20brewing.%20In%20his%20new%20avatar%2C%20Gandhi%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20unifier%20of%20dissent%20in%20the%20country%20and%20the%20pivot%20of%20peaceful%20political%20resistance.%20In%20universalising%20amon