sinessinsider.com%2Fwork-from-home-return-to-office-sexism-women-bosses-employees-2023-4%5C%22%3Eworking%20from%20home%20should%20be%20looked%20down%20upon%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20one%20new%20study%20could%20add%20some%20clarity%20to%20the%20competing%20views%3A%20It%20suggests%20that%20people%20are%20more%20productive%20working%20from%20the%20office%2C%20which%20could%20be%20good%20news%20for%20managers%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-ceos-remote-work-office-careers-2023-6%5C%22%3Etech%20companies%20trying%20to%20bring%20their%20employees%20back%20in%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nber.org%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2Fworking_papers%2Fw31515%2Fw31515.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20that's%20being%20circulated%20by%20the%20National%20Bureau%20of%20Economic%20Research%2C%20economists%20from%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20and%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20observed%20data-entry%20workers%20in%20Chennai%2C%20India%2C%20across%20two%20groups%20%E2%80%94%20those%20working%20from%20the%20office%20and%20those%20working%20from%20home%20%E2%80%94%20over%20test%20periods%20of%20eight%20weeks.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20finding%3F%20Those%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-from-home-productivity-hacks-2019-6%5C%22%3Ework-from-home%3C%2Fa%3E%20group%20were%2018%25%20less%20productive%20than%20those%20working%20from%20the%20office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20is%20%26quot%3Bproductivity%26quot%3B%20measured%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20gather%20subjects%20for%20the%20study%2C%20the%20researchers%20posted%20advertisements%20for%20entry-level%20data%20jobs%20in%20local%20newspapers%2C%20and%20ultimately%20observed%20a%20total%20of%20235%20workers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study.%20These%20workers%20were%20then%20divided%20into%20two%20groups%20that%20were%20randomized%20across%20skill%20level%20and%20preference%20for%20working%20from%20home%20or%20the%20office%20%E2%80%94%20among%20other%20traits%20%E2%80%94%20and%20given%20identical%20tasks%2C%20resources%2C%20and%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20noted%20that%20both%20groups%20were%20also%20asked%20to%20work%20for%20approximately%2035%20hours%20a%20week.%20However%2C%20those%20working%20from%20home%20were%20given%20the%20flexibility%20to%20choose%20when%20they%20worked%2C%20while%20those%20coming%20into%20the%20office%20were%20restricted%20to%20a%209%20a.m.%20to%205%20p.m.%20schedule.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20working%20from%20home%2C%20the%20researchers%20also%20took%20low-resolution%20pictures%20of%20the%20workers%20every%2015%20minutes%20through%20a%20camera%20built%20into%20a%20laptop%20they%20provided%2C%20to%20ensure%20they%20weren't%20outsourcing%20their%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20measure%20used%20to%20gauge%20productivity%20in%20the%20study%20was%20%26quot%3Bnet%20typing%20speed%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20the%20report%20defined%20as%20the%20number%20of%20correct%20entries%20typed%20per%20minute.%20The%20study%20also%20measured%20the%20%26quot%3Baccuracy%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20workers%20by%20comparing%20the%20ratio%20of%20correct%20data%20entries%20to%20total%20data%20entries%2C%20along%20with%20idle%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20data-entry%20workers%3F%20The%20report%20noted%20they're%20ubiquitous%20across%20India%2C%20the%20job%20doesn't%20require%20high-level%20skills%2C%20it%20can%20be%20easily%20performed%20in%20both%20remote%20and%20office%20settings%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-productivity-scores-dont-effectively-measure-employee-performance-2022-9%5C%22%3Ecollecting%20detailed%20measures%20of%20productivity%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20output%20for%20data-entry%20workers%20is%20a%20relatively%20straightforward%20process.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIt's%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20cultural%20norms%20in%20Chennai%2C%20India%2C%20are%20different%20from%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20or%20other%20places.%20David%20Atkin%2C%20one%20of%20the%20authors%20of%20the%20study%20who%20spoke%20to%20Fortune%20about%20the%20research%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F08%2F03%2Fremote-workers-less-productive-research%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexplained%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20in%20developing%20countries%20like%20India%2C%20homes%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bsmaller%2C%20more%20cramped%20and%20hot%2C%20and%20have%20noise%20pollution%2C%26quot%3B%20all%20of%20which%20are%20likely%20to%20affect%20productivity%20at%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWorking%20from%20home%20can%20make%20communication%20more%20challenging%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-remote-challenges-work-from-home-2019-10%5C%22%3Eremote%20workers%20could%20be%20less%20productive%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20their%20office%20counterpoints%20is%20because%20of%20challenges%20in%20communication%20that%20arise%20from%20virtual%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20earlier%20study%20of%20more%20than%2060%2C000%20staff%20members%20at%20Microsoft%20who%20transitioned%20from%20office%20work%20to%20remote%20work%20between%20December%202019%20and%20June%202020%20found%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-work-working-from-home-study-microsoft-meetings-2021-9%5C%22%3Eemployees%20became%20%26quot%3Bmore%20siloed%2C%20less%20dynamic%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20weren't%20able%20to%20form%20as%20many%20new%20connections%20compared%20to%20the%20pre-pandemic%20days.%20While%20people%20did%20form%20stronger%20connections%20with%20their%20immediate%20team%20members%2C%20the%20study%20found%20that%20they%20spent%20an%20average%20of%2025%25%20less%20ti