r.com%2F64d111b9f5d4870019e31bf7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwfh-work-from-home-decreases-productivity-18-percent-study-rto-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Data-entry%20workers%20in%20Chennai%2C%20India%2C%20were%20studied%20for%20eight%20weeks%20to%20find%20out%20if%20their%20productivity%20dropped%20when%20they%20worked%20from%20home.%20It%20did.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40insider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwfh-work-from-home-decreases-productivity-18-percent-study-rto-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20moved%20to%20a%20South%20Carolina%20island%20where%20there%20are%20no%20cars.%20It's%20like%20being%20transported%20back%20200%20years%20in%20time%2C%20but%20you%20can%20still%20get%20Instacart.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Upper%20left%20frame%3A%20An%20older%20man%20in%20a%20grey%20shirt%2C%20background%20image%3A%20a%20large%20two-storey%20house%20with%20front%20garden.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d10e7bf5d4870019e317a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJerry%20Jaskowiak%2C%20upper%20left%2C%20lives%20in%20an%20%24800%2C000%20home%20in%20Haig%20Point%2C%20a%20private%20community%20on%20Daufuskie%20Island%20in%20South%20Carolina.%3Cp%3EJerry%20Jaskowiak%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJerry%20Jaskowiak%20works%20remotely%20from%20Haig%20Point%20on%20Daufuskie%20Island%20in%20South%20Carolina.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDaufuskie%20Island%20is%20%26quot%3Bcar-free%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20only%20533%20residents.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%2062-year-old%20breaks%20down%20what%20living%20on%20the%20island%20is%20like.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20interview%20with%20Jerry%20Jaskowiak%2C%20a%2062-year-old%20company%20president%20who%20lives%20on%20a%20small%2C%20car-free%20island%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20South%20Carolina.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20lived%20on%20a%20car-free%20island%20that%20is%20less%20than%2010%20square%20miles%20for%20two%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20visited%20Daufuskie%20Island%20with%20some%20friends%20and%20loved%20the%20vibe%2C%20so%20she%20kept%20returning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20island%20is%20a%20unique%20and%20magical%20place.%20It's%20like%20going%20back%20200%20years.%20The%20dirt%20roads%20are%20lined%20with%20ancient%20oak%20trees%20and%20you%20can%20only%20get%20to%20the%20island%20via%20boat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20island%20captured%20my%20wife's%20imagination%20so%20much%2C%20she%20wanted%20to%20move%20here%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20want%20to%20move.%20We'd%20only%20recently%20finished%20renovating%20our%20house%20in%20Oldfield%2C%20South%20Carolina.%20My%20wife%20spent%20a%20year%20convincing%20me.%20The%20island's%20charm%2C%20beauty%2C%20and%20history%20made%20her%20feel%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20asked%20what%20would%20make%20this%20move%20an%20easy%20choice.%20I%20answered%3A%20%26quot%3B%241.3%20million%20for%20our%20house%2C%20one%20call%20with%20a%20realtor%2C%20and%20one%20viewing.%26quot%3B%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20impossible%20to%20sell%20our%20house%20so%20quickly%2C%20but%20we%20had%20a%20contract%20later%20that%20day%20%E2%80%94%20it%20felt%20like%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHaig%20Point%20is%20a%20private%20community%20where%20most%20of%20the%20population%20of%20Daufuskie%20Island%20live%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20part%20of%20Haig%20Point%20you%20have%20to%20pay%20an%20annual%20membership%20fee%20of%20%2425%2C660%2C%20or%20%2430%2C759%20if%20you%20want%20the%20golf%20membership%20that%20lets%20you%20golf%20essentially%20whenever%20you%20want%20%E2%80%94%20on%20top%20of%20a%20one-time%20initiation%20fee%20of%20%2450%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20Haig%20Point%2C%20I%20already%20lived%20in%20a%20community%20that%20had%20fees%20associated%20with%20living%20there.%20The%20fees%20are%20higher%20at%20Haig%20Point%20to%20cover%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20ferry%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20take%20much%20adjusting%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20membership%20covers%20the%20cost%20of%20staff%20and%20the%20amenities%20within%20the%20community.%20The%20community%20has%20a%2029-hole%20golf%20course%2C%20an%20outdoor%20pool%2C%20six%20tennis%20courts%2C%20a%20pickleball%20court%2C%20an%20equestrian%20center%2C%20and%20some%20other%20buildings%20that%20require%20upkeep%20%E2%80%94%20the%20membership%20pays%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20benefit%20of%20the%20membership%20is%20that%20you%20can%20get%20the%20boat%20to%20and%20from%20the%20island%20as%20often%20as%20you%20like%2C%20for%20free.%20A%20boat%20goes%20each%20way%20once%20an%20hour%20and%20you%20can%20bring%20guests%20with%20you%2C%20also%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHouses%20are%20a%20better%20value%20for%20your%20money%20on%20Haig%20Point%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20house%20we%20bought%20in%20Haig%20Point%20was%20cheaper%20than%20the%20one%20we%20sold.%20I%20think%20you%20get%20more%20house%20for%20the%20dollar%20here.%20That%20said%2C%20it%20costs%20a%20lot%20more%20to%20build%20or%20make%20renovations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20wanted%20to%20make%20some%20small%20changes%20to%20our%20new%20Haig%20Point%20house.%20Because%20there's%20no%20bridge%20access%20to%20the%20island%2C%20contractors%20have%20to%20take%20the%20boat%2030%20minutes%20each%20way.%20The%20contractor%20who%20began%20the%20renovation%20estimated%20it'd%20cost%20%24250%2C000%20for%20the%20job%2C%20we%20hit%20%24200%2C000%20halfway%20through%20and%20decided%20to%20finish%20the%20rest%20ourselves%20and%20spent%20about%20%24375%2C000%20in%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20island%20is%20considered%20%26quot%3Bcar-free%26quot%3B%20but%20you%20may%20see%20a%20few%20vehicles%20being%20used%20by%20maintenance%20staff.%20Haig%20Point%20has%20a%20big%20golf%20community%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20golf%20carts%20are%20the%20main%20form%20of%20transport%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20buy%20a%20nice%2C%20rebuilt%20golf%20cart%20from%20a%20dealer%20on%20the%20mainland%20for%20about%20%2411%2C000.%20We%20got%20one%20of%20those%20but%20also%20purchased%20a%20fancier%20one%20with%20hard%20doors%20to%20keep%20you%20warm%20when%20it%20gets%20chilly%20for%20around%20%2415%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EYou%20can%20still%20get%20Instacart%20and%20Starbucks%20on%20the%20island%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20always%20get%20asked%20where%20our%20groceries%20come%20from.%20We%20can%20either%20go%20to%20the%20mainland%20supermarket%20or%20order%20groceries%20online%20using%20Instacart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20delivery%20driver%20will%20bring%20your%20order%20to%20the%20boat%20terminal%20on%20the%20mainland%20and%20then%20the%20staff%20will%20bring%20it%20to%20the%20island.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20either%20pick%20it%20up%20from%20the%20Welcome%20Center%2C%20which%20is%20about%20five%20minutes%20from%20my%20house%2C%20or%20it%20can%20be%20delivered%20to%20your%20front%20door%20%E2%80%94%20for%20no%20extra%20cost%2C%20though%20we%20do%20tip.%20Because%20the%20Instacart%20guy%20is%20only%20delivering%20it%20on%20the%20mainland%2C%20the%20delivery%20fee%20is%20no%20more%20than%20if%20you%20lived%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20vendor%20from%20the%20mainland%20who%20runs%20a%20farmers%20market%20every%20Saturday%20selling%20produce%20and%20fish.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20small%2C%20independent%20restaurants%20on%20the%20island%20and%20even%20a%20Starbucks%20in%20the%20Welcome%20Center.%20Food%20on%20the%20island%20is%20slightly%20more%20expensive%20than%20on%20the%20mainland%2C%20with%20a%20markup%20of%20about%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWorking%20remotely%20from%20such%20a%20beautiful%20place%20has%20improved%20my%20work-life%20balance%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20work%20remotely%20as%20the%20president%20of%20an%20investment-accounting%20company.%20Internet%20connection%20is%20super%20important%20for%20me.%20I%20have%20to%20be%20on%20calls%20and%20frequently%20use%2050%20terabytes%20of%20cloud%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20the%20internet%20connection%20here%20is%20the%20most%20solid%20I've%20ever%20dealt%20with.%20I%20get%20a%20gigabyte%20download%20speed%20in%20my%20house%20for%20%24120%20a%20month.%20In%20my%20previous%20house%2C%20I%20was%20using%20the%20same%20company%20and%20I%20got%20half%20a%20gigabyte%20for%20%24100%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20worked%20remotely%20since%202014%2C%20so%20moving%20here%20really%20didn't%20change%20my%20work%20at%20all.%20Living%20here%20is%20really%20perfect%20for%20remote%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20I%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20commute%20to%20the%20mainland%20every%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20island%20has%20helped%20with%20my%20work-life%20balance.%20After%20work%2C%20I%20can%20walk%20down%20a%20winding%20road%20for%20five%20minutes%20and%20be%20able%20to%20look%20out%20across%20the%20Atlantic%20Ocean%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20pretty%20cool.%20Or%20I%20can%20go%20play%20a%20few%20holes%20of%20golf.%20It's%20so%20easy%20to%20step%20away%20from%20work%20and%20do%20something%20completely%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-south-carolina-island-no-cars-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691485606000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d10e7bf5d4870019e317a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-south-carolina-island-no-cars-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2062-year-old%20resident%20of%20Haig%20Point%20on%20Daufuskie%