quot%3BUnsurprisingly%2C%20consumers%20continue%20to%20attribute%20the%20challenging%20conditions%20to%20high%20home%20prices%20and%20unfavorable%20mortgage%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-price-outlook-homes-real-estate-investing-fannie-mae-survey-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691485192000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d1f9ae20f1cf0019ccb864%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-price-outlook-homes-real-estate-investing-fannie-mae-survey-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20out%20of%20five%20people%20say%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bbad%20time%20to%20buy%26quot%3B%20a%20new%20home%2C%20according%20to%20Fannie%20Mae%2C%20as%20mortgage%20rates%20soar%20and%20inventory%20levels%20stay%20low.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gglover%40insider.com%20(George%20Glover)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-price-outlook-homes-real-estate-investing-fannie-mae-survey-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%204%20Years%20Without%20Article%20370%20And%20Kashmir's%20Transformation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%205%20August%202019%2C%20by%20abrogating%20Article%20370%20and%2035A%20and%20bifurcating%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20let%20the%20world%20know%20%26quot%3Bimpossible%20is%20nothing%26quot%3B%20was%20not%20just%20a%20catchy%20tagline.%20However%2C%20deep%20down%2C%20the%20ruling%20establishment%20knew%20the%20task%20was%20only%20half%20done.%20There%20were%20many%20miles%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20had%20taken%20adequate%20measures%20to%20overcome%20any%20challenge%20-%20regional%2C%20national%20and%20international%2C%20particularly%20with%20relation%20to%20the%20two%20hostile%20neighbours.%20The%20legal%20and%20constitutional%20integration%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20had%20become%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20challenge%20now%20was%20the%20integration%20of%20people%20in%20Kashmir%20Valley%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2070%20years%2C%20people%20in%20the%20Valley%20were%20indoctrinated%20by%20regional%20and%20central%20leaders%20of%20various%20parties%2C%20except%20for%20the%20former%20Jan%20Sangh%20and%20the%20BJP.%20They%20were%20told%20that%20Article%20370%20was%20their%20armour%20against%20India%2C%20that%20they%20held%20special%20status%20because%20of%20protections%20granted%20under%20Article%20370.%20Generations%20of%20people%20had%20developed%20this%20psyche%20of%20Kashmir%20versus%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20cared%20to%20listen%20with%20an%20open%20mind%20about%20how%20discriminatory%20Article%20370%20was%2C%20even%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20benefiting%20only%20a%20handful%20and%20three%20modern%20day%20political%20dynasties%20in%20particular%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20speeches%20in%20both%20houses%20were%20among%20the%20finest%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20was%20right.%20A%20famed%20political%20advisor%20to%20a%20past%20regime%20had%20once%20narrated%20to%20this%20writer%20how%20over%20the%20years%2C%20conflict%20politics%20in%20Kashmir%20had%20mushroomed%20into%20cottage%2C%20medium%20and%20large%20industries%2C%20domestically%20and%20internationally.%20Entrenched%20beneficiaries%20wouldn't%20let%20that%20go%20at%20any%20cost%2C%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20generations%20of%20Kashmiris%20were%20brainwashed%20and%20incited%20into%20picking%20up%20stones%20and%20guns%20was%20brilliantly%20explained%20recently%20by%20Shah%20Faisal%2C%20a%20well-known%20Kashmiri%20bureaucrat-turned-politician-turned-bureaucrat.%20He%20shared%20his%20personal%20experiences%20as%20a%20Kashmiri%20and%20as%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20state%20--%20how%20young%20boys%20of%209-10%20years%20would%20pick%20up%20stones%20and%20sticks%20and%20enforce%20%26quot%3Bcurfew%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20directed%20by%20the%20masterminds.%20These%20kids%20would%20ask%20the%20elderly%20to%20show%20their%20ID%20cards%20and%20even%20attack%20them%20with%20sticks%20for%20violating%20%26quot%3Bcurfew%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EArticle%20370%20was%20abrogated%204%20years%20ago%20on%20August%205%2C%202019.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20this%20clip%2C%20IAS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshahfaesal%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40shahfaesal%3C%2Fa%3E%20describes%20why%20he%20changed%20his%20mind%20on%20370%2C%20how%20Pakistan%20gave%20rise%20to%20separatism%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20how%20the%20state%20has%20benefited%20from%20the%20abrogation.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFull%20podcast%20out%20tomorrow%20on%20Dostcast.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FkDG0vSPxT9%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FkDG0vSPxT9%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Sikandar%20(%40VinamreKasanaa)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVinamreKasanaa%2Fstatus%2F1687791074683801600%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20depth%20of%20the%20challenge%20before%20PM%20Modi%20after%20Article%20370%20was%20scrapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20confidence%20building%20measure%20came%20from%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20on%20August%207%2C%202019%3B%20he%20walked%20down%20the%20streets%20of%20Srinagar%20without%20security%20personnel%20glued%20to%20him%2C%20chatting%20with%20people%2C%20sharing%20a%20meal%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FSN0Vn_0dQeE%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20later%2C%20he%20visited%20Lal%20Chowk%2C%20Hazratbal%20Shrine%20and%20downtown%20Srinagar%20on%20Eid.%20That%20was%20to%20send%20the%20message%20that%20the%20government%20of%20India%20cared%20for%20ordinary%20people%20and%20there%20was%20nothing%20to%20fear.%20What%20had%20happened%20was%20for%20the%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20leadership%20at%20the%20Centre%20felt%20the%20need%20for%20a%20person%20in%20charge%20in%20Srinagar%20and%20Jammu%20to%20translate%20PM%20Modi's%20vision%20into%20reality%20-%20someone%20of%20integrity%2C%20motivation%20to%20do%20better%2C%20someone%20with%20an%20unassuming%20personality%20and%20charm%2C%20who%20was%20approachable%20and%20could%20easily%20connect%20with%20people.%20Manoj%20Sinha%2C%20a%20former%20Union%20Minister%2C%20appeared%20to%20fit%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20called%20from%20Varanasi%20to%20Delhi%20by%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20PM%20Modi%20and%20was%20immediately%20despatched%20to%20Srinagar%20as%20its%20new%20Lieutenant%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%207%20August%202020%2C%20Sinha%20assumed%20office.%20Besides%20other%20issues%2C%20Covid%20threw%20up%20a%20host%20of%20other%20challenges.%20Sinha%20picked%20up%20from%20where%20Doval%20had%20left.%20His%20first%20stop%20was%20the%20Government%20Medical%20College%20in%20Srinagar.%20The%20outreach%20was%20an%20instant%20hit%20with%20people.%20Some%20wrote%20on%20social%20media%20that%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20had%20done%20what%20chief%20ministers%20hadn't%20done%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20Sinha%20made%20it%20a%20habit%20to%20travel%20by%20road%20to%20every%20event.%20A%20chopper%20was%20a%20no-no%2C%20unless%20his%20destination%20was%20really%20far%20or%20there%20was%20some%20urgency.%20This%20made%20his%20ground%20understanding%20better%20and%20improved%20the%20people's%20perception%20of%20him.%20He%20went%20to%20areas%20seen%20to%20be%20hotbeds%20of%20terrorism.%20His%20recent%20presence%20at%20a%20Muharram%20procession%20(being%20held%20after%20over%20three%20decades)%20and%20his%20mingling%20with%20the%20gathered%20crowd%20surprised%20even%20critics%20of%20Modi%20government%20in%20the%20Valley.%20One%20can%20imagine%20how%20his%20security%20officers%20must%20have%20reacted%20to%20his%20decision%20to%20take%20such%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who%20has%20visited%20Kashmir%20before%20and%20after%202019%20can%20tell%20what%20has%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20there%20is%20still%20some%20scepticism%20among%20people%20in%20the%20Valley%20about%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20PM%20Modi%20and%20'LG%20Sarkar'%20are%20accepted%20and%20acceptable%20realities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20notorious%20Pattharbaji%20(stone%20pelting)%2C%20which%20destroyed%20the%20youth%20and%20the%20future%20of%20the%20younger%20lot%2C%20besides%20landing%20security%20personnel%20in%20dangerous%20scenarios%2C%20is%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%20No%20stone%20pelting%20incident%20has%20been%20reported%20since%20August%202019.%20There%20are%20many%20creative%20avenues%20for%20channeling%20the%20younger%20generation's%20energy%2C%20sporting%20arenas%20and%20opportunity%2C%20stadiums%20constructed%20across%20the%20Valley%2C%20skill%20development%20opportunities%2C%20self-help%20groups%2C%20schools%20and%20colleges%20and%20so%20on.%20The%20record%20tourist%20inflow%20has%20rehabilitated%20old%20businesses%20and%20greater%20connectivity%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20has%20sprouted%20new%20businesses%20and%20opportunities.%20Incidentally%2C%20women%20and%20girls%20are%20said%20to%20be%20more%20receptive%20to%20this%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20%26quot%3BBandh%20ka%20Bandh%20ho%20gaya%20(shutdowns%20have%20shut%20down)%26quot%3B.%20Bandh%20or%20shutdown%20had%20become%20a%20culture%20in%20the%20Valley%3B%20a%20bandh%20could%20be%20called%20by%20militants%20and%20separatists%20and%20terror%20outfits%20on%20anything%20or%20everything.%20This%20would%20manifest%20even%20more%20during%20any%20VVIP%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20July%202021%2C%20when%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20visited%20Kashmir%20on%20a%20three-day%20tour%2C%20the%20administration%20ensured%20there%20was%20no%20shutdown.%20Again%2C%20on%20August%205%20that%20year%20there%20was%20no%20shutdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20by%20Manoj%20Sinha%20at%20a%20public%20function%20was%20most%20noteworthy.%20When%20someone%20confronted%20him%20by%20saying%20that%20he%20used%20the%20Danda%20(stick)%20to%20ensure%20there%20was%20no%20bandh%2C%20he%20responded%20by%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20Pakistan%20and%20terror%20outfits%20could%20enforce%20shutdown%20by%20using%20the%20gun%2C%20what's%20wrong%20in%20use%20of%20danda%20by%20the%20administration%20to%20negate%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20local%20polls%20like%20the%20District%20Development%20Council%20elections%20and%20the%20Urban%20Body%20elections%20threw%20up%20new%20grassroots%20leaders%20of%20all%20hues%20who%20are%20more%20accessible%20and%20are%20alive%20to%20local%20concerns%20and%20aspirations.%20Roads%20and%20small%20bridges%20were%20built%20and%20electricity%20provided%20to%20areas%20that%20craved%20it%20for%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DDC%20election%20results%20were%20also%20a%20reflection%20of%20how%20popular%20faith%20in%20traditional%20parties%20had%20diminished.%20Ideally%20the%20People's%20Alliance%20for%20Gupkar%20Declaration%20(PAGD)%20comprising%20the%20National%20Conference%20(NC)%2C%20the%20People's%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%2C%20the%20CPI(M)%2C%20CPI%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20People's%20Conference%2C%20Awami%20National%20Conference%20and%20the%20People's%20Movement%2C%20should%20have%20swept%20the%20polls%2C%20not%20leaving%20any%20scope%20for%20rival%20parties%20or%20formations%2C%20but%20the%20results%20didn't%20go%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifth%2C%20the%20opening%20of%20cinema%20halls%2C%20music%2C%20lit%20fests.%20It%20took%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20the%20return%20of%20normalcy%20for%20cinema%20theatres%20to%20open%20in%20the%20Valley%20after%2033%20years.%20The%20first%20was%20a%20multiplex%20in%20Srinagar.%20More%20and%20more%20cinema%20halls%20followed%20in%20other%20districts.%20The%20reopening%20of%20cinema%20halls%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20resounding%20success%2C%20sending%20a%20strong%20message%20to%20those%20who%20wished%20to%20push%20Kashmiris%20into%20obscurantism%20and%20fundamentalism.%20So%20is%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20Jhelum%20River%20Front%2C%20which%20brought%20music%2C%20literature%20and%20enjoyment%20to%20life%20along%20Dal%20Lake%20and%20the%20Jhelum%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20successful%20conclusion%20of%20the%20G20%20tourism%20summit%20in%20Kashmir%20stands%20as%20a%20clear%20indication%20of%20what%20has%20changed.%20But%20even%20before%20that%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20inadvertently%20told%20the%20world%20how%20Kashmir%20has%20changed%20in%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20through%20their%20playful%20pictures%20and%20videos%20in%20Gulmarg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691485080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-10%2Fqg39gk78_kashmir-generic-journey-basket_625x300_13_October_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F4-years-without-article-370-and-kashmirs-transformation-4279405%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%205%20August%202019%2C%20by%20abrogating%20Article%20370%20and%2035A%20and%20bifurcating%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20let%20the%20world%20know%20%26quot%3Bimpossible%20is%20nothing%26quot%3B%20was%20not%20just%20a%20catchy%20tagline.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F4-years-without-article-370-and-kashmirs-transformation-4279405%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F4-years-without-article-370-and-kashmirs-transformation-4279405%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F4-years-without-article-370-and-kashmirs-transformation-4279405%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Why%20Didn't%20He%20Speak%20First%3F%5C%22%3A%20Minister's%20Dig%20At%20Rahul%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20dig%20at%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20asked%20why%20the%20Congress%20leader%20did%20not%20open%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20government%20today%20and%20said%20the%20treasury%20benches%20were%20%26quot%3Bvery%20enthusiastically%26quot%3B%20waiting%20for%20his%20speech.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comment%20invited%20an%20angry%20reaction%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20said%20the%20minister%20was%20revealing%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker's%20office%20and%20should%20refrain%20from%20doing%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi's%20status%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20was%20restored%20yesterday%20and%20the%20Congress%20had%20been%20pushing%20for%20it%20to%20happen%20early%20so%20he%20could%20participate%20in%20the%20debate.%20The%20Congress%20leader%20was%20present%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20called%20on%20Congress%20leader%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20to%20begin%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20motion%20at%20noon%2C%20Mr%20Joshi%2C%20who%20is%20the%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20minister%2C%20got%20up%20to%20say%20he%20had%20a%20point%20to%20make.%20Mr%20Joshi%20said%20that%2C%20as%20per%20his%20knowledge%2C%20the%20Speaker's%20office%20had%20received%20a%20letter%20at%2011.55%20am%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20would%20be%20speaking%20in%20place%20of%20Mr%20Gogoi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happened%20in%20the%20space%20of%20five%20minutes%2C%20sir%3F%20What%20is%20the%20problem%2C%20sir%3F%20We%20are%20very%20enthusiastic%20to%20listen%20to%20Mr%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Joshi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister's%20comments%20invited%20a%20sharp%20retort%20from%20Mr%20Gogoi%2C%20who%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BSpeaker%20sir%2C%20should%20we%20also%20reveal%20what's%20happening%20in%20your%20office%20and%20what%20requests%20are%20being%20received%3F%20You%20are%20the%20protector%20of%20this%20House.%20Should%20we%20also%20reveal%20what%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20said%20in%20your%20office%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20interrupted%20by%20an%20angry%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20said%20the%20Congress%20leader%20was%20levelling%20a%20serious%20allegation%20and%20he%20should%20reveal%20whatever%20he%20wanted%20to.%20The%20Home%20Minister%20was%20backed%20by%20Mr%20Joshi%2C%20who%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Mr%20Gogoi)%20cannot%20take%20the%20name%20of%20the%20PM%20and%20the%20Chair%20and%20level%20such%20baseless%20allegations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Gogoi%20said%20the%20Congress%20had%20always%20respected%20the%20confidentiality%20of%20everything%20that%20the%20Speaker%20told%20them%20in%20his%20office%2C%20Mr%20Birla%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20office%20is%20also%20part%20of%20the%20House.%20You%20should%20never%20make%20any%20comments%20that%20have%20no%20basis%20in%20fact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Joshi%20said%20he%20had%20simply%20revealed%20what%20was%20already%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20and%20had%20not%20let%20out%20any%20secrets.%20Hitting%20out%20at%20him%2C%20Mr%20Gogoi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20the%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20minister.%20You%20should%20remember%20your%20duties%20and%20not%20reveal%20what%20is%20said%20in%20the%20Speaker's%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20which%20has%20practically%20no%20chance%20of%20getting%20passed%2C%20is%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20opposition%20to%20compel%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20coalition's%20demand%20for%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20issue%20under%20Rule%20267%20and%20the%20government's%20refusal%20to%20do%20so%20have%20led%20to%20a%20logjam%20in%20both%20Houses%20of%20parliament%20since%20the%20monsoon%20session%20began%20on%20July%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20elected%20from%20the%20Wayanad%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20was%20reinstated%20in%20the%20parliament%20yesterday.%20On%20August%204%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20stayed%20his%20conviction%20in%20the%20criminal%20defamation%20case%20over%20the%20%26quot%3BModi%20Surname%26quot%3B%20remark%2C%20but%20maintained%20that%20his%20comments%20were%20not%20in%20good%20taste%2C%20especially%20for%20a%20person%20in%20public%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20had%20observed%20that%20the%20trial%20judge%20had%20awarded%20the%20maximum%20sentence%20of%20two%20years%20in%20the%20case%20and%20noted%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20would%20not%20have%20been%20disqualified%20if%20the%20period%20of%20sentence%20was%20even%20a%20day%20shorter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691484840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F189916v8_pralhad-joshi-650_625x300_08_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-didnt-he-speak-first-ministers-dig-at-rahul-gandhi-on-no-trust-debate-4279152%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Taking%20a%20dig%20at%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20asked%20why%20the%20Congress%20leader%20did%20not%20open%20the%20debate%20on%20th