elling%20myself%20to%20fake%20a%20smile%2C%20to%20repress%20my%20feelings...%20So%20that%20I%20grew%20up%20being%20slightly%20broken%20because%20I%20believed%20that%20only%20then%20people%20will%20love%20me.%20So%2C%20I%20systematically%20made%20sure%20that%20I%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20depressed%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Faamir-khan-had-this-much-fun-with-ira-junaid-and-azad-at-wimbledon-2023-final-4215251%5C%22%3EIra%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20her%20depression%20%26quot%3Bpartly%20genetic%26quot%3B%20and%20told%20ETimes%2C%20%26quot%3BDepression%20is%20a%20little%20complicated.%20It%20is%20partly%20genetic%2C%20partly%20psychological%2C%20and%20social.%20In%20my%20case%2C%20it%20is%20partly%20genetic.%20There%20is%20a%20history%20of%20mental%20health%20issues%20in%20my%20family%20on%20my%20mom%20and%20dad's%20side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIra%20added%20that%20her%20therapist%20told%20her%20that%20her%20parents%20Aamir%20Khan%20and%20Reena%20Dutta's%20divorce%20was%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20trigger%20points.%26quot%3B%20My%20therapist%20said%20that%20one%20of%20the%20trigger%20points%20was%20my%20parents%2C%20who%20handled%20their%20divorce%20as%20well%20as%20they%20could%20at%20that%20point.%20It%20was%20amicable.%20I%20am%20not%20blaming%20them%20but%20what%20they%20didn't%20realise%20is%20that%20because%20they%20made%20it%20seem%20like%20divorce%20was%20not%20a%20big%20deal%2C%20there%20was%20a%20perception%20my%20mind%20created%20of%20the%20situation.%20We%20create%20perceptions%20and%20we%20don't%20necessarily%20communicate%20to%20people%20about%20those%2C%26quot%3B%20Ira%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fira-khan-poses-with-nick-jonas-calls-it-teenage-fantasy-3915611%5C%22%3EIra%3C%2Fa%3E%20explained%20that%20she%20doesn't%20blame%20her%20parents%20for%20her%20depression%20and%20she%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%