ce-motion-updates-no-trust-vote-updates-sansad-tv-danish-ali-why-sansad-tvs-ticker-sparked-opposition-fury-during-no-confidence-debate-4279289%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-confidence-motion-updates-no-trust-vote-updates-sansad-tv-danish-ali-why-sansad-tvs-ticker-sparked-opposition-fury-during-no-confidence-debate-4279289%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20US%20government%20will%20add%20%245%20billion%20to%20its%20debt%20pile%20every%20single%20day%20for%20the%20next%20ten%20years%2C%20says%20analyst%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221765%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andrew%20Jackson%20portrait%20on%20twenty%20dollar%20bill.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d1068b20f1cf0019cbf9cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221324%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Government%20debt%20is%20predicted%20to%20rise%20to%20%2450%20trillion%20by%202033.%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20Fernandez%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFitch%20downgraded%20US%20credit%20for%20only%20the%20second%20time%20in%20the%20country's%20history%20last%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUS%20government%20debt%20is%20forecast%20to%20reach%20%2450%20trillion%20by%202033%2C%20per%20the%20CBO.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBofA's%20Michael%20Hartnett%20broke%20this%20down%20to%20%245.2%20billion%20every%20day%20for%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Fitch's%20US%20credit%20downgrade%2C%20one%20analyst%20has%20offered%20an%20ominous%20forecast%20for%20the%20outlook%20of%20government%20finances%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20research%20note%20published%20to%20investors%20Thursday%2C%20Bank%20of%20America's%20Michael%20Hartnett%20broke%20that%20down%20into%20one%20eye-watering%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20data%20from%20the%20Congressional%20Budget%20Office%2C%20an%20independent%20federal%20agency%2C%20that%20forecasts%20government%20debt%20will%20rise%20from%20%2432.5%20trillion%20now%20to%20%2450%20trillion%20by%202033%2C%20Harnett%20broke%20this%20down%20into%20US%20government%20debt%20rising%20by%20%245.2%20billion%20every%20single%20day%20for%20the%20next%20ten%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20equivalent%20of%20giving%20every%20single%20American%20citizen%20%2415%20each%20morning.%20Or%2C%20about%20half%20the%20sum%20Jeff%20Bezos%20added%20to%20his%20personal%20fortune%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20CBO%20report%2C%20debt%20will%20jump%20from%2098%25%20of%20U.S.%20gross%20domestic%20product%20to%20181%25%20by%202053%2C%20rivaling%20ratios%20seen%20only%20during%20Second%20World%20War%20and%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFitch's%20downgrading%20was%20only%20the%20second%20time%20the%20US%20has%20experienced%20a%20dent%20in%20its%20creditworthiness.%20The%20last%20time%20was%20in%202011.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20downgrade%20comes%20after%20the%20government%20hit%20its%20%2431.4%20trillion%20borrowing%20limit%20in%20January%20%E2%80%93%20brokering%20an%20aversion%20in%20the%2011th-hour%20to%20raise%20the%20debt%20ceiling.%20It%20expects%20to%20have%20to%20borrow%20another%20%241%20trillion%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202023%20alone.%20Under%20the%20current%20laws%2C%20this%20fiscal%20hole%20shows%20no%20sign%20of%20narrowing%20over%20the%20long-term.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20high%20and%20rising%20debt%20would%20slow%20economic%20growth%2C%20push%20up%20interest%20rates%20to%20foreign%20holders%20of%20U.S.%20debt%2C%20and%20pose%20significant%20risks%20to%20the%20fiscal%20and%20economic%20outlook%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CBO%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20last%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-debt-5-billion-every-day-for-next-10-years-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22publish