%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F08%2F04%2Fus%2Fus-tourist-killed-italy-boating-accident%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Eoutlet%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported%20that%20Ms%20Vaughan%20was%20thrown%20into%20the%20water%20and%20died%20after%20being%20injured%20by%20the%20sailing%20boat's%20propeller.%20She%20was%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20water%20onto%20a%20dock%2C%20but%20by%20the%20time%20emergency%20crews%20arrived%2C%20she%20was%20pronounced%20dead%20at%20the%20scene.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Vaughan's%20husband%2C%20Mike%20White%2C%20suffered%20dislocated%20shoulder%20and%20cuts%20to%20his%20arms%2C%20while%20their%20two%20children%2C%20aged%2012%20and%208%2C%20were%20not%20physically%20harmed%20but%20were%20left%20in%20severe%20shock%20after%20witnessing%20the%20tragic%20crash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBloomsbury%20Publishing%20is%20very%20sad%20to%20confirm%20reports%20of%20the%20death%20of%20Adrienne%20Vaughan%2C%20President%20of%20Bloomsbury%20USA%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20injuries%20sustained%20in%20a%20boat%20collision%20in%20Italy%20on%20Thursday.%20Her%20husband%20and%20two%20children%20survived%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20publishing%20house%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomsbury.com%2Fus%2Fconnect%2Flatest-news%2Fadrienne-vaughan%2F%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20loss%20of%20Adrienne%20is%20a%20terrible%20blow.%20Since%20she%20was%20appointed%20President%20of%20Bloomsbury%20USA%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20America%20has%20grown%20to%20become%20our%20biggest%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20why%20the%20speedboat%20Ms%20Vaughan%20and%20her%20family%20were%20on%20collided%20with%20the%20sailboat.%20Italian%20prosecutors%20in%20Salerno%20have%20launched%20an%20investigation%20into%20her%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nd