narratives%20about%20%26quot%3Bthe%20death%20of%20democracy%26quot%3B%20and%20free%20speech%20in%20India%20are%20aimed%20at%20stalling%20the%20country's%20progress%20and%20are%20emerging%20mostly%20from%20within%20the%20country%2C%20former%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%20Harish%20Salve%20has%20said%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20NDTV's%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%20as%20part%20of%20a%20special%20series%20to%20mark%20the%2076th%20Independence%20Day%2C%20Harish%20Salve%20also%20explained%20India's%20strong%20push%20for%20the%20extradition%20of%20Nirav%20Modi%20and%20Vijay%20Mallya%2C%20tying%20in%20with%20the%20ongoing%20negotiations%20on%20a%20Free%20Trade%20Agreement%20(FTA)%20with%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20anti-entrepreneurial%20mindset%20of%20%26quot%3Bvested%20interests%26quot%3B%2C%20Harish%20Salve%20said%20today%20courts%20were%20being%20used%20by%20countries%20to%20try%20and%20stall%20India's%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20perception%20of%20India%20is%20changing%2C%20and%20no%20country%20would%20like%20any%20country%20to%20outpace%20them.%20For%20example%2C%20our%20biggest%20'friend'%20China%20-%20India%20is%20in%20direct%20economic%20conflict%20with%20it%20-%20these%20countries%20try%20to%20use%20the%20courts%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Salve%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20sought%20after%20lawyers%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20can%20say%20anything%20about%20India's%20economic%20progress.%20So%2C%20a%20narrative%20is%20created%20about%20India%20-%20%26quot%3Bdemocracy%20is%20dead%20in%20India%26quot%3B.%20That%20you%20are%20able%20to%20stand%20in%20India%20and%20say%20'democracy%20is%20dead'%20is%20biggest%20proof%20that%20democracy%20is%20alive...Unfortunately%2C%20the%20narrative%20is%20being%20created%20mostly%20from%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20at%20the%20negotiating%20table%20%26quot%3Bon%20equal%20footing%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20UK%20on%20a%20Free%20Trade%20Agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20trade%20talks%20taking%20more%20time%20than%20expected%2C%20Mr%20Salve%20said%20in%20its%20efforts%20to%20bring%20back%20fugitives%20like%20Nirav%20Modi%20and%20Vijay%20Mallya%2C%20India%20was%20pushing%20the%20UK%20to%20accelerate%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20in%20the%20UK%20is%20that%20the%20first%20step%20to%20extradition%2C%20which%20is%20judicial%2C%20is%20done%20for%20both%20Nirav%20Modi%20and%20Vijay%20Mallya.%20The%20final%20step%20has%20to%20be%20taken%2C%20now%20that%20all%20legal%20steps%20are%20completed.%20But%20now%20there%20is%20some%20asylum%20claim...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20engaged%20in%20hard%20negotiations%20for%20the%20FTA%20and%20its%20stance%20was%20correct.%20%26quot%3BToday%20we%20are%20at%20the%20negotiating%20table%20on%20equal%20terms%2C%20so%20it%20is%20taking%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20lawyer%20said%20UK's%20eagerness%20to%20sign%20the%20FTA%20with%20India%20was%20inconsistent%20with%20the%20delay%20over%20sending%20fugitives%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20whenever%20there%20is%20a%20high-level%20meeting%2C%20(Prime%20Minister%20Narendra)%20Modi%20asks%2C%20'Where%20are%20they%3F%20Why%20should%20UK%20become%20the%20home%20for%20Indian%20fugitives%3F'.%20Then%20they%20(UK)%20talk%20about%20FTA%20with%20India.%20It%20is%20inconsistent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wide-ranging%20interview%2C%20Mr%20Salve%20also%20talked%20about%20the%20recent%20Supreme%20Court%20reprieve%20for%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20allegations%20of%20the%20Congress%20using%20freebies%20for%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20language%20used%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20his%20%26quot%3BModi%20surname%26quot%3B%20comment%20was%20exceptionally%20disrespectful%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20to%20suspend%20the%20Congress%20leader's%20conviction%20was%20driven%20not%20by%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20case%20but%20by%20concerns%20for%20his%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20should%20be%20convicted%20or%20not%20is%20a%20different%20issue.%20But%20the%20highly%20disrespectful%20manner%20of%20talking...%20you%20are%20making%20false%20accusations%20and%20then%20you%20say%20I%20am%20in%20public%20life...Everyone%20knows%2C%20however%20much%20he%20denies%20it%2C%20he%20dreams%20of%20becoming%20prime%20minister.%20Is%20this%20his%20stature%20to%20use%20this%20sort%20of%20language%3F%26quot%3B%20Harish%20Salve%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSupreme%20Court%20judges%20said%20what%20he%20said%20was%20wrong%20and%20it%20is%20not%20right%20to%20talk%20like%20this.%20But%20the%20conviction%20was%20stayed%20because%20the%20constituency%20should%20not%20go%20unrepresented%20until%20there%20is%20a%20decision%20on%20his%20appeal%20(against%20conviction).%20That%20is%20why%20it%20was%20stayed%2C%20not%20on%20merits%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Salve%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Salve%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20politics%20of%20freebies%2C%20calling%20the%20freebie%20culture%20the%20%26quot%3Bworst%20kind%20of%20politics%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20form%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20distortion%2C%20it%20is%20a%20type%20of%20corruption.%20You%20give%20out%20the%20taxpayer's%20money%20with%20both%20hands%2C%20to%20win%20an%20election.%20There%20cannot%20be%20worse%20politics%20than%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Salve%20said%2C%20citing%20the%20Congress's%20five-guarantee%20promise%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKarnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20told%20MLAs...%20we%20can't%20do%20your%20development%20projects%20as%20we%20have%20to%20fulfill%20promises....Taxpayer's%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%20is%20being%20spent%20on%20those.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691482260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fj5s6bbn_hairsh-salve-ndtv-interview_625x300_08_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffalse-narrative-on-democracy-created-mostly-within-india-harish-salve-4279268%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22False%20narratives%20about%20%26quot%3Bthe%20death%20of%20democracy%26quot%3B%20and%20free%20speech%20in%20India%20are%20aimed%20at%20stalling%20the%20country's%20progress%20and%20are%20emerging%20mostly%20from%20within%20the%20country%2C%20former%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%20Harish%20Salve%20has%20said%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffalse-narrative-on-democracy-created-mostly-within-india-harish-salve-4279268%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffalse-narrative-on-democracy-created-mostly-within-india-harish-salve-4279268%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffalse-narrative-on-democracy-created-mostly-within-india-harish-salve-4279268%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Woman%20With%20Nut%20Allergy%20Forced%20To%20Buy%2048%20Packets%20Of%20Peanuts%20On%20Flight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2027-year-old%20woman%20named%20Leah%20William%20has%20claimed%20she%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20buy%20up%20every%20single%20packet%20of%20peanuts%20on%20her%20flight%20from%20Germany%20to%20London%20after%20the%20cabin%20crew%20refused%20to%20ban%20them%20on%20board.%20Ms%20Williams%20spent%20144%20euros%20(approximately%20Rs%2013%2C088)%20even%20after%20being%20severely%20allergic%20to%20them.%20She%20bought%20all%2048%20packets%20of%20nuts%20onboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Ftravel%2Fnews-and-advice%2Fpeanuts-allergy-woman-eurowings-flight-b2389262.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndependent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20cost%20was%20almost%20three%20times%20the%20price%20of%20the%2050%20euros%20airfare%20she%20paid%20for%20her%20budget%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20design%20firm%20worker%20from%20Hampshire%20didn't%20want%20anyone%20opening%20a%20packet%20of%20peanuts%20while%20she%20was%20inside%20the%20aircraft.%20According%20to%20the%20media%20outlet%2C%20Ms%20Williams%20had%20once%20broken%20out%20in%20hives%20after%20someone%20had%20opened%20a%20bag%20of%20peanuts%20near%20her%20on%20a%20flight.%20She%20was%20not%20ready%20to%20take%20any%20chances%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Williams%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-news%2Fi-spent-150-every-packet-30636823%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMirror%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20the%20airline%20should%20be%20ashamed%20of%20how%20they%20handled%20the%20situation%20and%20she%20is%20now%20requesting%20a%20refund%20for%20the%20nuts%20she%20purchased%20onboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Eurowings%20spokesperson%20told%20the%20Independent%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20very%20sorry%20that%20the%20flight%20with%20us%20did%20not%20go%20as%20smoothly%20as%20planned%20and%20we%20regret%20any%20inconvenience%20this%20has%20caused%20Leah%20Williams.%20One%20thing%20in%20advance%3A%20Leah%20Williams%20was%20not%20forced%20to%20buy%20all%20packages%20of%20peanuts%20on%20board%20-%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%20our%20purser%20tried%20to%20offer%20her%20an%20alternative%20solution%20by%20informing%20all%20passengers%20sitting%20around%20her%20about%20Leah's%20allergy.%20She%20agreed%20at%20first%20but%20then%20decided%20to%20still%20buy%20all%20the%20packages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20added%20that%20it%20was%20unable%20to%20guarantee%20the%20aircraft%20is%20free%20of%20foodstuffs%20that%20may%20trigger%20allergic%20reactions%20such%20as%20peanuts%20as%20passengers%20sometimes%20bring%20their%20own%20food%20onboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20there%20are%20many%20causes%20for%20allergies%20and%20intolerances%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20exclude%20the%20possibility%20of%20their%20presence%20on%20board%20a%20plane%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%20%26quot%3BFurthermore%2C%20due%20to%20its%20construction%20(shape%2C%20air%20conditioning%20system%2C%20ventilation%2C%20etc.)%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20prevent%20an%20accumulation%20of%20peanut%2Fnut%20traces%20(e.g.%20residues%20from%20an%20earlier%20flight)%20despite%20regular%20and%20thorough%20cleaning%20of%20the%20aircraft.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20has%20urged%20passengers%20that%20they%20should%20bring%20their%20allergy%20medication%20in%20their%20hand%20luggage%20and%20inform%20cabin%20crew%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20medically%20trained%20cabin%20crew%20always%20has%20access%20to%20medication%20to%20provide%20emergency%20medical%20care%20in%20the%20event%20of%20an%20intolerance%20or%20allergic%20shock%20on%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691482200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ff45kv82_peanuts-unsplash_625x300_08_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-woman-with-severe-nut-allergy-forced-to-buy-48-packets-of-peanuts-on-flight-4279267%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ms%20Williams%20spent%20144%20euros%20(approximately%20Rs%2013%2C088)%20even%20after%20being%20severely%20allergic%20to%20peanuts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-woman-with-severe-nut-allergy-forced-to-buy-48-packets-of-peanuts-on-flight-4279267%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-woman-with-severe-nut-allergy-forced-to-buy-48-packets-of-peanuts-