s%20have%20complained%20that%20some%20of%20those%20Bills%20were%20not%20properly%20debated%20and%20oftentimes%20not%20even%20referred%20to%20parliamentary%20committees%20%E2%80%93%20sparking%20fears%20about%20the%20setting%20of%20negative%20precedents%20in%20the%20South%20Asian%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EControversial%20legislation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20four%20Bills%20%E2%80%93%20which%20have%20since%20become%20law%20%E2%80%93%20were%20singled%20out%20for%20specific%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Army%20(Amendment)%20Act%20proposes%20up%20to%20five%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20those%20who%20disclose%20sensitive%20information%20pertaining%20to%20the%20security%20of%20the%20country%20or%20the%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Official%20Secrets%20Amendment%20Bill%20grants%20blanket%20powers%20to%20intelligence%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%20and%20the%20E-Safety%20Bill%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20media%20organizations%20to%20obtain%20tax%20and%20other%20detailed%20information%20on%20individuals%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20government%20officials%20and%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20these%20Bills%20sailed%20through%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20parliament%2C%20especially%20the%20lower%20house%2C%20or%20National%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Official%20Secrets%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20lower%20house%20but%20faced%20fierce%20resistance%20in%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20upper%20house%2C%20the%20Senate%2C%20when%20it%20landed%20there%20a%20few%20days%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20was%20passed%20on%20Sunday%20but%20only%20after%20it%20had%20been%20amended%20to%20address%20the%20concerns%20of%20some%20senators%20and%20other%20stakeholders%20who%20forced%20the%20government%20to%20refer%20the%20Bill%20to%20a%20Senate%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20significant%20amendment%20was%20th