700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20in%20the%20final.%20For%20the%20cricketing%20universe%2C%20it's%20the%20captain-coach%20pairing%20of%20Hardik%20Pandya%20and%20Ashish%20Nehra%20that%20has%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20the%20franchise's%20early%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20Indian%20T20%20team%2C%20Parthiv%20feels%20Hardik%20isn't%20getting%20the%20sort%20of%20support%20he%20needs%20from%20head%20coach%20Dravid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20a%20couple%20of%20instances%20about%20Hardik%20Pandya's%20captaincy%20which%20have%20been%20glaring%20mistakes.%20The%20first%20was%20giving%20that%20over%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Axar%20Patel%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63024-akshar-rajeshbhai-patel-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAxar%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20first%20game%20when%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Nicholas%20Pooran%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1720-nicolas-pooran-playerprofile%5C%22%3ENicholas%20Pooran%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20come%20out%20to%20bat.%20And%20today%2C%20this%20one%20(not%20giving%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yuzvendra%20Chahal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1394-yuzvendra-chahal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYuzvendra%20Chahal%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%204th%20over%20in%20the%202nd%20T20I).%20Hardik%20Pandya%20the%20captain%20has%20been%20brilliant%20with%20GT%20but%20at%20Gujarat%20Titans%20he%20had%20the%20support%20of%20Ashish%20Nehra.%20But%20is%20Rahul%20Dravid%20the%20proactive%20coach%20or%20person%20which%20we%20are%20looking%20for%20in%20the%20T20%20format.%20I%20don't%20think%20so.%20In%20my%20mind%2C%20we%20need%20someone%20who%20is%20proactive.%20Hardik%20Pandya%20has%20that%20spark%20but%20he%20needs%20that%20support%2C%20which%20to%20me%20Rahul%20Dravid%20doesn't%20provide%2C%26quot%3B%20Parthiv%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3