000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102524447%2Cimgsize-31434.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fmore-sports%2Fathletics%2Fhow-much-can-we-teach-the-kids-find-the-source-of-doping-stop-it-from-there-anju-bobby-george%2Farticleshow%2F102523938.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anju%20Bobby%20George%20is%20the%20epitome%20of%20performing%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20when%20we%20talk%20about%20India%20in%20athletics.%20It%20took%20India%2019%20years%20to%20win%20another%20World%20Championships%20medal%20in%20track%20and%20field%2C%20after%20Anju%20did%20it%20in%202003%20with%20her%20long-jump%20bronze.%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20won%20a%20silver%20medal%20last%20year.%20But%20what%20pains%20India's%20long-jump%20queen%20are%20the%20short-term%20gains%20that%20young%20athletes%20are%20lured%20by%20thereby%20getting%20eventually%20caught%20in%20the%20doping%20net.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22JASPREET%20SAHNI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fmore-sports%2Fathletics%2Fhow-much-can-we-teach-the-kids-find-the-source-of-doping-stop-it-from-there-anju-bobby-george%2Farticleshow%2F102523938.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Violence%3A%20SC%20Constitutes%20Judicial%20Commission%20to%20Examine%20Probes%2C%20Suggest%20Remedial%20Measures%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F09134529%2Faa-Cover-au7mok02br0m258dgrfuqgmvt0-20200611145151.Medi_.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%2C%20August%207%2C%20constituted%20an%20all-women%20judicial%20committee%20to%20examine%20the%20ongoing%20probes%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20the%20state%20police%20into%20incidents%20of%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20will%20be%20headed%20by%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20high%20court%20Chief%20Justice%20Gita%20Mittal%20and%20will%20also%20comprise%20retired%20Justices%20Shalini%20Joshi%20and%20Asha%20Menon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Flitigation%2Fsupreme-court-contempt-of-court-case-pil-petitioner-1-lakh-costs%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20committee%20will%20have%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbroad-based%20function%20of%20examining%20the%20ongoing%20probes%20and%20suggesting%20remedial%20measures%2C%20compensation%20and%20rehabilitation%20among%20other%20things%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20was%20set%20up%20by%20a%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20and%20Justices%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20while%20hearing%20a%20batch%20of%20pleas%20regarding%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20have%20been%20ongoing%20for%20more%20than%20three%20months%20now.%20Among%20the%20petitioners%20were%20two%20women%20from%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20community%20who%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-5-policemen-suspended-over-viral-video-of-sexual-assault%5C%22%3Eparaded%20naked%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20a%20mob.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20committee%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20not%20supplant%20the%20CBI%20but%20is%20being%20constituted%20to%20ensure%20faith%20in%20rule%20of%20law%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20Bar%20%3Cem%3Eand%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20court%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20broad%20outline%20is%20to%20use%20whatever%20in%20our%20power%20is%20to%20restore%20faith%20in%20rule%20of%20law.%20We%20will%20appoint%20a%20committee%20of%203%20former%20HC%20judges.%20This%20committee%20of%20three%20judges%20will%20look%20at%20the%20investigation%2C%20relief%2C%20remedial%20measures%2C%20compensation%20and%20rehabilitation.%20It%20is%20a%20broad-based%20committee..%20it%20will%20look%20at%20the%20relief%20camps%20(also).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20turned%20down%20the%20request%2C%20made%20by%20some%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20to%20transfer%20the%20trial%20in%20the%20cases%20outside%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20not%20supplant%20the%20CBI%20since%20it%20is%20looking%20at%20it.%20But%20to%20ensure%20faith%20in%20rule%20of%20law..%20we%20are%20not%20casting%20aspersion%20on%20CBI%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20court%20said%20that%20the%20probe%20by%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20will%20be%20looked%20into%20by%20former%20Maharashtra%20DGP%20and%20NIA%20officer%20Dattatray%20Padsalgikar.%20He%20will%20%E2%80%9Chead%20another%20layer%20of%20supervision%E2%80%9D%20and%20will%20report%20back%20to%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-member%20judicial%20committee%20and%20Padsalgikar%20will%20submit%20their%20respective%20reports%20to%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20court%20also%20set%20out%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinvestigation%20hierarchy%E2%80%9D%20for%20probes%20by%20the%20CBI%20and%20state%20SIT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20CBI%20probes%2C%20the%20court%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20proposing%20to%20direct%20that%20there%20shall%20be%205%20officers%20of%20rank%20at%20least%20DySP%20who%20will%20be%20brought%20into%20CBI%20from%20various%20states%20and%20we%20will%20ask%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20from%20the%20states%20where%20Hindi%20is%20spoken%20and%20have%205%20officers%20to%20be%20brought%20on%20deputation%20to%20the%20CBI%20to%20oversee%20the%20investigation%20into%20these%20FIRs.%20These%20officers%20will%20also%20function%20within%20four%20corners%20of%20administrative%20set%20up%20of%20the%20CBI%20and%20will%20be%20supervised%20by%20joint%20director%20of%20CBI.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20state%20SITs%2C%20it%20added%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20will%20be%20about%2042%20SITs%20which%20will%20look%20at%20cases%20not%20transferred%20to%20CBI.%20One%20inspector%20from%20that%20state%20will%20also%20be%20brought%20in%20by%20MHA%20in%20those%2042%20SITs%20so%20that%20one%20officer%20outside%20the%20State%20is%20there%20in%20each%20of%20those%20cases.%20These%2042%20SITs%20should%20be%20supervised%20by%206%20DIG%20Rank%20officers%20from%20outside%20the%20State%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%A6%20each%20officer%20will%20oversee%206%20SITs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691475938000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F09134529%2Faa-Cover-au7mok02br0m258dgrfuqgmvt0-20200611145151.Medi_.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanipur-violence-sc-judicial-commission-examine-probes-remedial-measures%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20all-women%20committee%20will%20be%20headed%20by%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20high%20court%20Chief%20Justice%20Gita%20Mittal%20and%20will%20also%20comprise%20retired%20Justices%20Shalini%20Joshi%20and%20Asha%20Menon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanipur-violence-sc-judicial-commission-examine-probes-remedial-measures%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%2090%20PTI%20workers%20arrested%20for%20protesting%20Imran%20Khan's%20arrest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691475889000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102524332%2Cimgsize-104830.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fover-90-pakistan-tehreek-e-insaf-workers-arrested-for-protesting-imran-khans-arrest%2Farticleshow%2F102521569.cms%22%2C%22summary