9CWe%20walked%20out%20because%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20charges%20against%20him.%20It%20was%20a%20mark%20of%20protest%20against%20such%20individuals%2C%20however%20senior%2C%20not%20respecting%20women%20and%20having%20used%20their%20position%20of%20power%20to%20wipe%20off%20their%20sins%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chaturvedi%20told%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHerald%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcji-ranjan-gogoi-rajya-sabha-nomination%5C%22%3Enominated%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gogoi%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20barely%20four%20months%20after%20he%20retired%20as%20CJI%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20decision%20had%20received%20criticism%2C%20as%20Gogoi%20during%20his%20time%20as%20CJI%20had%20headed%20benches%20in%20cases%20key%20to%20the%20same%20government%20that%20nominated%20him.%20These%20include%20the%20Ayodhya%20land%20title%20case%2C%20the%20Rafale%20case%2C%20the%20case%20of%20the%20dismissal%20of%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20director%20Alok%20Verma%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20time%20as%20MP%2C%20Gogoi%20has%20not%20asked%20a%20single%20question%20in%20parliament%20so%20far%2C%20nor%20introduced%20any%20private%20member%E2%80%99s%20Bill%2C%20it%20had%20been%20reported%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20earlier%20reported%20on%20Gogoi%E2%80%99s%20silence%20in%20parliament%20and%20low%20attendance%20to%20notice%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-sealed-cover-mp-the-track-record-of-former-cji-ranjan-gogoi-in-parliament%5C%22%3Ein%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20again%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwill-project-views-of-judiciary-in-parliament-said-ranjan-gogoi-three-years-on-hes-yet-to-speak%5C%22%3Ein%202022%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFamously%2C%20in%202021%2C%20when%20asked%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2