2https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102517341.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EChina%20has%20criticised%20Russia%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bbrutal%20and%20excessive%20law-enforcement%20activities%26quot%3B%20against%20Chinese%20citizens%20at%20a%20border%20checkpoint%20with%20Kazakhstan.%20Despite%20being%20unusually%20harsh%2C%20such%20comments%20do%20not%20signify%20a%20broader%20shift%20in%20Beijing's%20view%20of%20Russia%20since%20China%20has%20repeatedly%20sought%20to%20create%20some%20space%20with%20Moscow%20on%20issues%20such%20as%20the%20use%20of%20nuclear%20weapons%20and%20attacks%20on%20civilians.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchinas-rare-russia-rebuke-doesnt-mean-xi-jinping-is-ditching-putin%2Farticleshow%2F102517341.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchinas-rare-russia-rebuke-doesnt-mean-xi-jinping-is-ditching-putin%2Famp_articleshow%2F102517341.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchinas-rare-russia-rebuke-doesnt-mean-xi-jinping-is-ditching-putin%2Famp_articleshow%2F102517341.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gyanvapi%20Is%20a%20Litmus%20Test%20for%20the%20Sanctity%20of%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act.%20Our%20System%20Failed%20It.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F18123926%2F2022_5img17_May_2022_PTI05_17_2022_000125B-min.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20a%20new%20phenomenon%20that%20a%20mosque%E2%80%99s%20fate%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI).%20Mostly%2C%20the%20executive%20has%20used%20the%20ASI%20to%20regulate%20the%20religious%20activities%20of%20Muslims%20in%20old%20mosques.%20Many%20a%20times%2C%20the%20courts%20have%20handed%20over%20their%20fate%20to%20the%20ASI%20by%20assigning%20it%20a%20certain%20role%20to%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20is%20the%20same%20institution%20which%20has%20stopped%20the%20offering%20of%20namaz%20in%20many%20undisputed%20mosques%20throughout%20the%20country.%20It%20has%20either%20kept%20its%20control%20over%20them%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Eunder%20the%20Ancient%20monuments%20And%20Archeological%20Sites%20and%20Remains%20Act%2C%201959%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20other%20notifications%20issued%20from%20time%20to%20time%20%E2%80%93%20or%20left%20them%20to%20be%20used%20for%20the%20entertainment%20of%20elites%20or%20lovers%20(contrary%20to%20the%20religious%20character%20of%20the%20premises).%20Here%2C%20the%20ASI%20made%20some%20or%20the%20other%20rules%20which%20go%20against%20the%20very%20essentials%20of%20offering%20namaz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20case%2C%20the%20ASI%20was%20handed%20over%20the%20assignment%20of%20giving%20a%20report.%20The%20outcome%20of%20its%20report%20wrongly%20settled%20the%20public%20narrative%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%E2%80%99s%20demolition%20prior%20to%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201528%20%E2%80%93%20the%20same%20public%20narrative%20that%20shifted%20the%20course%20of%20history%20with%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20the%20same%20ASI%20that%20has%20been%20tasked%20with%20checking%20the%20religious%20character%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid.%20The%20offering%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enamaz%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20currently%20allowed%2C%20without%20any%20assurance%20as%20to%20whether%20in%20view%20of%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%2C%201991%2C%20the%20character%20of%20the%20masjid%20and%20the%20practice%20of%20offering%20namaz%20here%20will%20see%20changes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solicitor%20general%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fgyanvapi-mosque-case-sc-records-assurance-for-arrangements-for-wuzu-on-eid-1211781.html%5C%22%3Estatement%20was%20recorded%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20namaz%20shall%20continue%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20refresh%20some%20lessons%20from%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Funderstanding-the-gyanvapi-mosque-dispute-what-does-the-places-of-worship-act-say%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20Case%3A%20What%20Does%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20Say%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20affidavit%20of%20the%20then-chief%20minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Kalyan%20Singh%20(the%20undertaking%20given%20by%20the%20state%20of%20UP)%2C%20which%20was%20recorded%20in%20the%20order%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F17698471%2F%5C%22%3Eas%20stating%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpending%20a%20final%20solution%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20will%20hold%20itself%20fully%20responsible%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janma%20Bhumi-Babri%20Masjid%20structures%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20ensued%20from%20such%20an%20assurance%20is%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contempt%20proceedings%20arising%20out%20of%20this%20clear%20breach%20of%20undertaking%20recorded%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%20could%20not%20be%20taken%20up%20for%20its%20final%20hearing%20despite%20advocate%20Rajiv%20Dhavan%2C%20who%20represented%20the%20Muslim%20side%2C%20pushing%20for%20its%20listing%20during%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F10105517%2Fcats-275-300x169.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F10105517%2Fcats-275-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F10105517%2Fcats-275-1024x577.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F10105517%2Fcats-275.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-395480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22169%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFormer%20UP%20chief%20minister%20and%20Rajasthan%20governor%20Kalyan%20Singh.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20the%20contempt%20proceedings%20were%20taken%20up%20for%20final%20hearing%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20two%20things%20had%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20Kalyan%20Singh%20died%20on%20August%2028%2C%202021%2C%20which%20made%20the%20contempt%20proceedings%20against%20him%20infructuous.%20Second%2C%20in%202019%2C%20a%20five%20judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20finally%20decided%20the%20dispute%20in%20favour%20of%20Ram%20temple%20and%20gave%20an%20option%20to%20the%20Muslim%20party%20to%20avail%20alternate%20land%20for%20mosque.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20land%20was%20given%20by%20the%20state%20of%20UP%20to%20the%20UP%20Waqf%20Board%20%E2%80%93%20more%20than%2020%20kms%20from%20the%20place%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20once%20existed%20for%20about%20400%20years.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Babri%20Masjid%20might%20have%20become%20a%20chapter%20in%20the%20history%20books%20of%20India.%20But%20Gyanvapi%20is%20the%20present.%20As%20they%20say%2C%20history%20repeats%20itself%2C%20and%20so%20is%20happening%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20In%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20case%2C%20again%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fits-controversial-to-call-gyanvapi-a-mosque-yogi-adityanath%2Farticleshow%2F102291862.cms%5C%22%3Ehas%20spoken%3C%2Fa%3E%20completely%20against%20the%20character%20of%20the%20mosque%20while%20the%20matter%20is%20being%20examined%20simultaneously%20at%20all%20the%20three%20levels%20of%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20only%20overreach%20into%20judicial%20process%2C%20but%20also%20aimed%20to%20set-out%20and%20strengthen%20the%20narrative%20contrary%20to%20the%201991%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20we%20not%20only%20have%20the%20%3Cem%3EPlaces%20of%20Worship%20Act%2C%201991%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0we%20have%20the%20affirmation%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20itself%20that%20the%20Act%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20basic%20features%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fayodhya-verdict-do-not-convert-religious-character-of-places-of-worship-supreme-court%2Farticle61621480.ece%5C%22%3Ehad%20observed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Act%20is%20an%20affirmation%20of%20the%20solemn%20duty%20which%20was%20cast%20upon%20the%20state%20to%20preserve%20and%20protect%20the%20equality%20of%20all%20faiths%20as%20an%20essential%20constitutional%20value%2C%20a%20norm%20which%20has%20the%20status%20of%20being%20a%20basic%20feature%20of%20the%20constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgyanvapi-mosque-judiciary-dispute%5C%22%3EBy%20Allowing%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20Survey%2C%20SC%20Has%20Turned%20a%20Blind%20Eye%20Towards%20Injustice%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20allowing%20the%20ASI%20survey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-allows-asi-survey-of-gyanvapi-mosque-without-excavation-or-damage-to-structure-using-non-invasive-process-234398%5C%22%3Eduring%20the%20pendency%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20petition%20challenging%20the%20maintainability%20of%20the%20suit%2C%20what%20is%20at%20stake%2C%20one%20may%20ask%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20the%20ASI%20survey%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20institutionalise%20the%20%E2%80%98public%20narrative%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20same%20public%20narrative%20that%20became%20instrumental%20in%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20the%20mere%20carrying%20out%20of%20the%20ASI%20survey%20casts%20aspersions%20on%20the%20character%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20%E2%80%93%20a%20structure%20that%20is%20%E2%80%98disputed%E2%80%99%20and%20needing%20a%20scientific%20study%20to%20establish%20its%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20crucial%20to%20be%20reminded%20that%20the%20object%20of%20the%201991%20Act%20was%20to%20preserve%20the%20religious%20character%20of%20a%20place%20of%20worship%20as%20it%20existed%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947.%20By%20allowing%20the%20ASI%20survey%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%2C%20not%20only%20has%20the%20religious%20character%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20been%20put%20into%20dispute%2C%20but%20the%20objective%20of%20the%201991%20Act%20has%20vanished%20into%20thin%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201991%20Act%20had%20kept%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20case%20as%20an%20exception%20from%20its%20application.%20The%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20second-largest%20matter%20before%20the%20courts%20related%20to%20the%20questioning%20of%20a%20masjid%E2%80%99s%20character%20post-Babri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeedless%20to%20mention%2C%20the%20dispute%20also%20has%20its%20deep%20roots%20in%20the%20political%20promises%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%20Gyanvapi%2C%20thus%2C%20was%20the%20litmus%20test%20to%20ascertain%20the%20relevance%20of%20the%201991%20Act%20and%20the%20sanctity%20of%20judgement%20on%20it%2C%20a%20test%20in%20which%20our%20system%20has%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Fauthor%2FM.R.-Shamshad%5C%22%3EM.R.%20Shamshad%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20advocate%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691461857000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F18