manoeuvres%2C%20insertion%20into%20the%20lunar%20orbit%2C%20separation%20of%20the%20lander%2C%20a%20set%20of%20deboost%20manoeuvres%20and%20a%20power%20descent%20phase%20for%20a%20soft%20landing%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20P%20Veeramuthuvel%2C%20project%20director%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20spacecraft%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20Mission%3A%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20orbit-raising%20maneuver%20(Earth-bound%20perigee%20firing)%20is%20performed%20successfully%20from%20ISTRAC%2FISRO%2C%20Bengaluru.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20spacecraft%20is%20expected%20to%20attain%20an%20orbit%20of%20127609%20km%20x%20236%20km.%20The%20achieved%20orbit%20will%20be%20confirmed%20after%20the%20observations.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20next%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FLYb4XBMaU3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FLYb4XBMaU3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1683767962560512000%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%2C%20the%20spacecraft%20will%20go%20around%20the%20Moon%20to%20reduce%20its%20velocity%20in%20orbit%20and%20prepare%20for%20a%20soft%20landing%20on%20its%20surface.%20This%20orbiting%20will%20continue%20till%20Chandrayaan-3%20reaches%20a%20circular%20orbit%20of%20100%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20this%20is%20achieved%2C%20the%20lander%20and%20rover%20will%20descend%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F216483%2Fiisc-isro-moon-lunar-soil-simulant-space-brick-eco-friendly-homes-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurface%20of%20the%20Moon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20being%20separated%20from%20the%20propulsion%20module.%20Chandrayaan-3%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%20the%20Moon%E2%80%99s%20surface%20by%2023%20August%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20Mission%20Update%3A%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELunar%20Orbit%20Insertion%20(LOI)%20maneuver%20was%20completed%20successfully%20today%20(August%2005%2C%202023).%20With%20this%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FChandrayaan3%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Chandrayaan3%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20successfully%20inserted%20into%20a%20Lunar%20orbit.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20next%20Lunar%20bound%20orbit%20maneuver%20is%20scheduled%20tomorrow%20(August%2006%2C%202023)%2C%20around%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FIC3MMDQMjU%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FIC3MMDQMjU%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20LVM3-M4%2FCHANDRAYAAN-3%20MISSION%20(%40chandrayaan_3)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchandrayaan_3%2Fstatus%2F1687831700452098048%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20successful%20completion%2C%20India%20will%20become%20the%20fourth%20country%20to%20achieve%20a%20lunar%20soft%20landing%20after%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20former%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20and%20China.%20Both%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20former%20Soviet%20Union%20failed%20many%20times%20before%20they%20successfully%20landed%20on%20the%20Moon.%20China%20was%20the%20only%20country%20to%20succeed%20in%20its%20first%20attempt%20with%20the%20Chang%E2%80%99e-3%20mission%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691408722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D326455%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20lunar%20mission%20launched%20by%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%2C%20recently%20shared%20some%20stunning%20captures%20of%20the%20