%20me%20a%20lot%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUmer%20shares%20these%20tips%20for%20future%20aspirants%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20important%20thing%20that%20every%20aspirant%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20is%20to%20learn%20everything%20that%20the%20NCERT%20books%20offer.%20Many%20times%2C%20aspirants%20focus%20only%20on%20the%20notes%20got%20from%20coaching%20classes%2C%20but%20that%20will%20not%20cover%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CFocus%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300235%2Fupsc-cse-prelim-where-you-can-get-ncert-books-free-download%2F%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20NCERT%20syllabus%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20you%20will%20easily%20get%20good%20marks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20advises%20them%20to%20revise%20everything.%20%E2%80%9CMake%20thorough%20notes%20and%20bullet%20points.%20Then%20keep%20revising%20them%20so%20everything%20remains%20fresh%20in%20your%20head.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20acknowledges%20that%20preparing%20for%20the%20exam%20can%20be%20stressful.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20exams%20and%20preparing%20for%20it%20can%20make%20you%20anxious.%20However%2C%20I%20always%20tried%20to%20keep%20myself%20calm%20and%20focused%20on%20the%20material%20rather%20than%20the%20result.%20My%20parents%20would%20always%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20give%20your%20100%20percent%20effort%2C%20good%20results%20will%20come%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20I%20wholeheartedly%20believed%20in%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fumer-3-1690810755.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Umer%20worked%20as%20a%20painter%20to%20support%20his%20family%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fumer-3-16908